thread.title: Hunterdon Central seniors earn N.J. Seal of Biliteracy
thread.title_full: Hunterdon Central seniors earn N.J. Seal of Biliteracy

author: Craig Turpin | NJ Advance Media for NJ.com
title: Hunterdon Central seniors earn N.J. Seal of Biliteracy
text: Hunterdon Central Regional High School announced that 100 senior students in the Class of 2017 have earned the New Jersey Seal of Biliteracy for attaining a high level of proficiency in speaking, reading, and writing in one or more foreign languages in addition to English.
